Second of all, my referance to rotations is not a moot point simply because *if* you have ever engaged a mob that was on rotation, you have benefitted of the conventions of the server and can no longer try to exclude yourself from those conventions when they don't suit you. The fact that the mob we are currently in a frenzy over is *not* on rotation, is not relevent to the discussion, as the conventions of that camp are well known, and claiming otherwise is bordering on willful blindness and is still inexcusable. <br>
